## 🔒 Safety & Guardrails

### Immutable Rules
- Hard constraints NEVER relaxed (enforced via ConstraintValidator)
- Baseline EAs NEVER auto-modified (safe in baseline_and_info/)
- Configuration NEVER bypasses validation (Pydantic enforced)
- Test fixtures NEVER deleted (for regression testing)

### Rollback Safety
- All generated strategies in `strategies/generated/` (safe)
- All historical results in PostgreSQL (safe)
- All analysis reports in `reports/analysis/` (safe)
- Original EAs in `baseline_and_info/` (safe)

### Code Quality
- Type hints on all functions (Pydantic + Python typing)
- Comprehensive docstrings on all methods
- Unit tests for critical functionality
- Real-world test fixtures (not mock data)

